org.ga4gh.ComplianceFramework

Class Requests

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ga4gh.ComplianceFramework.Requests

  • public class Requests
extends java.lang.Object
    Class containing methods used to implement REST calls using REST Assured. These methods are be used by test cases to fire requests at REST servers and receive responses.
